description:
The ultimate burgundy eyeshadow palette. Maybelline Burgundy Bar Eyeshadow Palette includes 12 rich, high-pigment shades for infinite burgundy looks.

Maybelline Burgundy Bar Eyeshadow Palette features warm notes of burgundy perfectly curated with amber pigments and rose-gold nudes. Ultra-blendable pigments create infinite sensuous looks. 13 looks in one palette - use as duos, trios or quads.

12 eyeshadows in burgundy, amber and rose-gold shades

High pigment formula with superior blendability

Create multiple eyeshadow looks with one palette

Contains both matte and metallic finishes

Create duo, trio or quad designs.
name: Maybelline Burgundy Bar Eyeshadow Palette 9.6G
